NOTE ON DATA

This repository contains NO NANOGrav data. The real 15-year data set is
downloaded at setup time from the NANOGrav collaboration's public repository
(github.com/nanograv/15yr_stochastic_analysis) and from Zenodo
(doi:10.5281/zenodo.8423265). That data is the property of the NANOGrav
Collaboration and is subject to its own terms and citation requirements; see
Agazie et al. 2023, ApJL 951 L9 and ApJL 951 L8.
